    oc:hasArgumentHint "competitor names (1-5), your company name" ;
    oc:hasCategory "marketing" ;
    oc:hasDescription "Research your competitors and build an interactive battlecard. Outputs an HTML artifact with clickable competitor cards and a comparison matrix. Trigger with \"competitive intel\", \"research competitors\", \"how do we compare to [competitor]\", \"battlecard for [competitor]\", or \"what's new with [competitor]\"." ;
